hadiths[14]{hadithnumber,text}:
3736,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ruqba nafiz ho jaeyga.
3737,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ruqba mustaqil taur par usi shakhs key liye bana diya jisey wo diya gaya tha.
3738,"shayad Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, unhoney farmaya : ruqba wapis nahin aayega, chunanche jo shakhs kisi ko koi chiz ruqba dega to wo chiz us shakhs ki meeras ban jaeygi."
3739,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney maal ruqba ki surat mein na do ( kyonkey wo wapis nahin milengey) lekin agar kisi shakhs ney koi chiz ruqba key taur par di to wo usi ki rahegi jis ko us ney di.
3740,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : umra usi shakhs key liye mustaqil ho jaeyga jisey diya gaya. aur ruqba bhi mustaqil taur par usi shakhs ko milega jisey diya gaya. aur hiba ko wapis leney wala apni qai chaatney waley ki tarah hai.
3741,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke umra aur ruqba barabar hain (wapis nahin ayengey.)
3742,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : ruqba aur umra halal nahin. jisey koi chiz bator umra di gaee, wo usi ki rahegi aur jis shakhs ko koi chiz bator ruqba di gaee, wo bhi usi ki rahegi."
3743,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke umra aur ruqba durust nahin. jis shakhs ko umra diya gaya ya ruqba diya gaya, wo usi key paas rahega jisey umra ya ruqba diya gaya. uski zindagi mein bhi aur marney key baad bhi. (yani uskey warison ko muntaqil ho jaeyga). us hadees ko hanzala bin abi Sufiyan jamhi ney mursal bayan kya hai."
3744,Hazrat Taoos (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ruqba halal nahin. jis shakhs ko ruqba diya jaeyga to is mein virasat jari hogi (aur wo wapis nahin aayega).
3745,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : umra virasat ban jaeyga.
3746,Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : umra warison ko mil jaeyga. ( deney waley ko wapis nahin milega ).
3747,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : umra mustaqil taur par nafiz ho jaeyga.
3748,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : umra warison ko mil jaeyga.
3749,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : umra warison ko mil jaeyga. « wallahu-aalam » .
